<lb n="0178c01" ed="T"/>毘闍那咩　莎呵</p>
<lb n="0178c02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0178c0201">世尊此陀羅尼句。為一切眾生作護作救。護
<lb n="0178c03" ed="T"/>持是人悉皆令得安隱寂靜。令離衰惱滅諸
<lb n="0178c04" ed="T"/>惡毒。離諸苦惱王難賊難怨憎之難。若天龍
<lb n="0178c05" ed="T"/>鬼神羅剎夜叉鳩槃<app type="star" corresp="#0178007"><lem wit="【大】">茶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">荼</rdg></app>復多那阿跋漆羅呿
<lb n="0178c06" ed="T"/>屈陀。如是等所觸惱者。所侵損者悉得除滅。
<lb n="0178c07" ed="T"/>又復世間一切諸毒。<note n="0178018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">芳＝若【三】</note><note n="0178018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">芳＝若【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0178018"><lem wit="【大】">芳</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">若</rdg></app>草若木<note n="0178019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">根＋（莖）【三】</note><note n="0178019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">根＋（莖）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0178019"><lem wit="【大】">根</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">根莖</rdg></app>華果。衣
<lb n="0178c08" ed="T"/>裳飲食世間之物。及<app type="star" corresp="#0178004"><lem wit="【大】">蟲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">虫</rdg></app>鳥禽獸諸能為毒惡
<lb n="0178c09" ed="T"/>傷人者。悉令消壞不能為<note n="0178020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">惡＋（毒惡傷人者悉令消壞不能為惡）十三字【三】</note><note n="0178020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惡＋（毒惡傷人者悉令消壞不能為惡）十三字【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0178020"><lem wit="【大】">惡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">惡毒惡傷人者悉令消壞不能為惡</rdg></app>。又復虛空日月
<lb n="0178c10" ed="T"/>星辰。旋嵐風輪鬼神起風。欲來傷人諸鬼神
<lb n="0178c11" ed="T"/>等。欲來求食吸人精氣食人肉血者。令人疫
<lb n="0178c12" ed="T"/>病熱病。若一日二日三日四日乃至七日。或
<lb n="0178c13" ed="T"/>令冷病風<note n="0178021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔病〕－【三】</note><note n="0178021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔病〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0178021"><lem wit="【大】">病</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>濕病<note n="0178022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">寒＋（病）【三】</note><note n="0178022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">寒＋（病）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0178022"><lem wit="【大】">寒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">寒病</rdg></app>冷等病。若身內若身
<lb n="0178c14" ed="T"/>外一切眾病。若七日若十六日悉令消滅不
<lb n="0178c15" ed="T"/>能為害。是等諸鬼神若以手若以口若以脚。
<lb n="0178c16" ed="T"/>若以舌若以心欲惱人<note n="0178023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔者〕－【三】</note><note n="0178023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔者〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0178023"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。及以惡人欲為人
<lb n="0178c17" ed="T"/>作惱害者。先當誦此呪力能<note n="0178024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">噤＝禁【元】【明】</note><app n="0178024"><lem wit="【大】">噤</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">禁</rdg></app>持。令彼惡人
<lb n="0178c18" ed="T"/>惡鬼噤碎失念不令為惡。世尊我今當更<note n="0178025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔說〕－【三】</note><note n="0178025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔說〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0178025"><lem wit="【大】">說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0178c19" ed="T"/>神呪以守護之。</p>
<lb n="0178c20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0178c2001" cb:type="dharani">阿車阿車<note place="inline">瞋彌<app type="star" corresp="#0178017"><lem wit="【大】">反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">切</rdg></app></note>　牟尼牟尼　摩訶牟尼牟尼䉛
<lb n="0178c21" ed="T"/><note place="inline">烏<note n="0178026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">力＝刀【三】</note><note n="0178026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">力＝刀【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0178026"><lem wit="【大】">力</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">刀</rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0178017"><lem wit="【大】">反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">切</rdg></app></note>　尼休休　摩訶那迦休休　鬪伽那知
<lb n="0178c22" ed="T"/>阿呼阿伽那知阿多那知　阿吒阿吒　那吒
<lb n="0178c23" ed="T"/>那吒　留豆　留豆　留豆　休休豆留　唏
<lb n="0178c24" ed="T"/><app type="star" corresp="#0178015"><lem wit="【大】">泥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">埿</rdg></app>唏<app type="star" corresp="#0178015"><lem wit="【大】">泥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">埿</rdg></app>唏<app type="star" corresp="#0178015"><lem wit="【大】">泥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">埿</rdg></app>唏<app type="star" corresp="#0178015"><lem wit="【大】">泥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">埿</rdg></app>　郁仇摩仇摩　仇摩
<lb n="0178c25" ed="T"/>　仇摩　唏梨唏梨唏梨　唏<note n="0178027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">梨＋（埿）【三】</note><note n="0178027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">梨＋（埿）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0178027"><lem wit="【大】">梨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">梨埿</rdg></app>　尼利
<lb n="0178c26" ed="T"/>　尼利　摩訶尼利莎訶</p>
<lb n="0178c27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0178c2701">此陀羅尼為受持讀誦者作護。若有鬼食人
<lb n="0178c28" ed="T"/>精氣。若損人資產耗人財物。如是一切眾怖
<lb n="0178c29" ed="T"/><note n="0178028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">怨＝恐【三】</note><note n="0178028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">怨＝恐【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0178028"><lem wit="【大】">怨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">恐</rdg></app>等悉為結界。今為某國某甲合家無量作
<pb n="0179a" xml:id="T21.1237.0179a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0179a01" ed="T"/>大擁護。今當重更說防諸惡<note n="0179001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔呪〕－【三】</note><note n="0179001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔呪〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0179001"><lem wit="【大】">呪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>即說呪曰。</p>
<lb n="0179a02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0179a0201" cb:type="dharani">留牟　留牟　留牟　留牟　留摩留摩　留
<lb n="0179a03" ed="T"/>摩留摩　唏梨唏梨　唏梨唏梨　唏梨唏梨
<lb n="0179a04" ed="T"/>　仇那仇那　仇那　仇那　仇那　仇㝹仇
<lb n="0179a05" ed="T"/>㝹　<note n="0179002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">仇＝休【宋】＊</note><note n="0179002" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: ＊-->仇＝休【宋】＊</note><app n="0179002"><lem wit="【大】">仇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">休</rdg></app>㝹　仇㝹　仇留仇留　<note n="0179003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔仇留〕－【宋】＊</note><app n="0179003"><lem wit="【大】">仇留</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0179a06" ed="T"/>　<app type="star" corresp="#0179003"><lem wit="【大】">仇留</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>　休婁　休婁　休婁　休婁　唏梨
<lb n="0179a07" ed="T"/>暮休　暮休　暮休暮休　暮唏梨暮唏梨
<lb n="0179a08" ed="T"/>　暮唏梨暮唏梨　休牟　休牟　休牟休<note n="0179004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">摩＋（摩）【三】</note><note n="0179004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">摩＋（摩）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0179004"><lem wit="【大】">摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">摩摩</rdg></app>
<lb n="0179a09" ed="T"/><note n="0179005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔休〕－【三】</note><note n="0179005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔休〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0179005"><lem wit="【大】">休</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>咩提　摩咩思摩阿提迦羅咩兜　莎訶</p>
<lb n="0179a10" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0179a1001">爾時大將重白佛言。世尊此呪極有神力如
<lb n="0179a11" ed="T"/>上所說。莫令持此呪者。有王畏賊畏火畏水
<lb n="0179a12" ed="T"/>畏。風毒刀兵等畏。日月星辰鬼神等畏。或有
<lb n="0179a13" ed="T"/>餘惡知識心生忿<note n="0179006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">姤＝妬【三】</note><note n="0179006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">姤＝妬【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0179006"><lem wit="【大】">姤</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">妬</rdg></app>意生惡害。欲相侵惱者。
<lb n="0179a14" ed="T"/>當先誦此呪為其結界。當令彼惡鬼惡人仇
<lb n="0179a15" ed="T"/>怨之人心生侵惡者。令其愚癡迷悶噤碎。自
<lb n="0179a16" ed="T"/>遇眾惡不越此界。不能侵犯誦此呪者。世尊
<lb n="0179a17" ed="T"/>若有善男子善女人誦此呪者。一切天龍阿
<lb n="0179a18" ed="T"/>修羅諸惡鬼神人非人等。皆悉隨侍擁護不
<lb n="0179a19" ed="T"/>令遇惡。世尊我是鬼神大將。<note n="0179007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔力〕－【三】</note><note n="0179007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔力〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0179007"><lem wit="【大】">力</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>能降伏一
<lb n="0179a20" ed="T"/>切諸<note n="0179008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">惡＋（惡）【三】</note><note n="0179008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惡＋（惡）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0179008"><lem wit="【大】">惡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">惡惡</rdg></app>鬼。若有誦此呪者。我當將諸鬼神
<lb n="0179a21" ed="T"/>晝夜不離。擁護其人令不見惡。不令惡鬼惡
<lb n="0179a22" ed="T"/>人得其便也。若侵損惱害誦此呪者。我當以
<lb n="0179a23" ed="T"/>千<note n="0179009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">輻輪＝輪輻【三】</note><note n="0179009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">輻輪＝輪輻【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0179009"><lem wit="【大】">輻輪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">輪輻</rdg></app><note n="0179010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">轢＝礫【宋】</note><app n="0179010"><lem wit="【大】">轢</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">礫</rdg></app>碎其頭。令諸鬼神為作衰害。世
<lb n="0179a24" ed="T"/>尊此呪極有神力極有威德。唯願流布施眾
<lb n="0179a25" ed="T"/>安樂。世尊誦此呪者。其人德力唯佛知之。世
<lb n="0179a26" ed="T"/>尊此大神呪應付賢德有智善人。若不能誦
<lb n="0179a27" ed="T"/>者。應以好紙書寫盛以綵囊。著種種香常持
<lb n="0179a28" ed="T"/>隨身。若有憂怖恐難。常當憶念此呪無不消
<lb n="0179a29" ed="T"/>滅。世尊若有事難憂怖惡鬼神惡夢。欲令消
<pb n="0179b" xml:id="T21.1237.0179b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0179b01" ed="T"/>滅<note n="0179011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔者〕－【三】</note><note n="0179011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔者〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0179011"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。先當結界使諸惡不起。令彼惡人惡
<lb n="0179b02" ed="T"/>鬼惡賊自受其殃。身體燋枯心意狂亂。欲結
<lb n="0179b03" ed="T"/>界之時。應淨洗浴著淨衣服好淨塗地。安七
<lb n="0179b04" ed="T"/>器漿飲。二器著少血<note n="0179012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">飲二＝一【三】</note><note n="0179012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飲二＝一【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0179012"><lem wit="【大】">飲。二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">一</rdg></app>器著種種漿飲然
<lb n="0179b05" ed="T"/>八燈。燒熏陸香運心供養。我將諸鬼神至其
<lb n="0179b06" ed="T"/>邊施<note n="0179013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">其＋（人）【三】</note><note n="0179013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">其＋（人）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0179013"><lem wit="【大】">其</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">其人</rdg></app>所願。其人應誦此呪結赤縷然後持
<lb n="0179b07" ed="T"/>行。即能消除一切諸難。</p>
<lb n="0179b08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0179b0801">爾時佛告阿難。此呪極有大神力。能消除一
<lb n="0179b09" ed="T"/>切諸難并諸<note n="0179014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔時〕－【三】</note><note n="0179014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔時〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0179014"><lem wit="【大】">時</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>惡。擁護眾生多所利益。汝
<lb n="0179b10" ed="T"/>好受持廣令流布。若<note n="0179015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔有〕－【三】</note><note n="0179015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔有〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0179015"><lem wit="【大】">有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>城邑村落誦此呪者
<lb n="0179b11" ed="T"/>莫不蒙利。若有國王大臣誦此呪者。其人境
<lb n="0179b12" ed="T"/>土無有惡賊怖難。災橫疾疫水旱風霜。若遇
<lb n="0179b13" ed="T"/>惡賊應誦此呪。若繫著高幢頭。賊見此<note n="0179016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">幢＝憧【宋】</note><app n="0179016"><lem wit="【大】">幢</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">憧</rdg></app>
<lb n="0179b14" ed="T"/>賊尋退散降伏。阿難此呪極有神力。極有<note n="0179017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">大＋（威）【三】</note><note n="0179017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">大＋（威）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0179017"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">大威</rdg></app>
<lb n="0179b15" ed="T"/>德。應令四眾善誦持之。爾時眾會聞佛所說
<lb n="0179b16" ed="T"/>歡喜奉行。</p>
<lb n="0179b17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0179b1701"><note n="0179018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔此中…結〕三十七字－【三】</note><note n="0179018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔此中…結〕三十七字－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app cb:word-count="37" n="0179018"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">此中丹本有注云。牛屎作場外灰緣竪二刀十二隻箭。請婆拘法餘如前。部誦三遍結縷十二結</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0179b18" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead><title><note n="0179019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（佛說）＋阿【宋】</note><app n="0179019"><lem wit="【大】">阿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">佛說阿</rdg></app>吒婆拘<note n="0179020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔鬼神…尼〕九字－【宋】</note><app cb:word-count="9" n="0179020"><lem wit="【大】">鬼神大將上佛陀羅尼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note n="0179021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔神呪〕－【元】【明】</note><app n="0179021"><lem wit="【大】">神呪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note n="0179022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">經＋（出廣濟眾生經第一卷中）細註【元】</note><app n="0179022"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">經<note place="inline">出廣濟眾生經第一卷中</note></rdg></app></title></cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
